# Admin Panel UX & Workflow Strategy (Locked)

> **Status:** PHASE 5 - LOCKED
> **Purpose:** To define the Admin Panel as the "SEO Operating System" of the platform.

---

## 1. Core Philosophy
*   **The Brain:** The Admin Panel decides *everything*. The frontend is a passive display.
*   **SEO OS:** It's not just for writing text; it's for managing the site's relationship with search engines.
*   **UX Pattern:** Consistency is king. All distinct content types (Sites, Blogs, News) share the **same** editing flow.

---

## 2. Global Layout Structure
A standard, professional dashboard layout.

*   **Left Sidebar:** Navigation modules (Collapsible).
*   **Top Bar:** User Profile, Role Badge (`SUPER ADMIN`), Logout, Global Search.
*   **Main Content:** The workspace.

### Sidebar Navigation Tree
```
Dashboard          (Overview & SEO Health)

Betting Sites      (The "Money" Modules)
  â”œâ”€ All Sites
  â”œâ”€ Add New Site
  â””â”€ Reviews

